channel.title: Silabsoft error need help!
channel.description:
Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading Silab Client
To fix this try the following (in order )
1: Try closing ALL open web browser windows, and reloading
2: Try clearing your web-browser cache from tools>internet options
3: Try useing a different game-world
4: Try re-booting your computer
5: Try selecting a different version of Java from the play game menu
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
